    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the orzo has been cooking for 5 min, add the<strong> halved green beans</strong> and cook, covered, for a further 5 min</p><p>Add the <strong>halved Tenderstem</strong> and cook, covered, for 5 min further or until everything's tender with a slight bite</p><p>Tip: Add a splash more water if your orzo is looking a little dry, and stir it occasionally to prevent it from sticking</p>",
      "order": 6,
