    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lemony orzo primavera</strong> topped with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated Italian cheese</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, the <strong>toasted pine nuts</strong> and season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Garnish with a<strong> lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
